features: Ideal for Plant Placing in aquariums
description: Plant Tongs are a versatile tool for any fish keeper. Can be used to plant new aquarium plants in your substrate. You can add plants without sticking your arm in the water. The tongs aren't just for planting though. They can be used for creating coral reefs and positioning corals on your live rocks. You can also use the handy tongs for removing debris.
